{"tid":1466661,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"今晚又有好撚多五毛","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:50:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:51:39.000Z","uid":262346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c592f19879fc0a16efcb7c612d21f4fe3b1d5eff","tid":1466661,"uid":262346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:50:58.000Z","msg":"第一<br />\n<br />\n分化post<br />\n就幾句野 <br />\n屌機場手足做得唔岩<br />\n<br />\n我再重申和理非同勇武缺一不可<br />\n不分化 不割席 <br />\n無論示威者做乜我地都要撐<br />\n因為呢個係民主運動<br />\n想佢成功就唔好屌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二<br />\n<br />\n有鬼論<br />\n就算有鬼做激進野又如何<br />\n我地控制唔到佢地<br />\n發現到鬼就綁<br />\n審佢 <br />\n搵唔到鬼都無計<br />\n<br />\n總之鬼做既任何野都係加快左民主運動<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第三<br />\n<br />\n影響人論<br />\n<br />\n試問史上任何民運 邊個唔影響人<br />\n機場既旅客好少數<br />\n<br />\n如果依家為攬炒既話<br />\n呢件事上到國際新聞<br />\n又怕咩影響人<br />\n<br />\n果d咩法國旅客 土耳其母女 我理閪得你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總之和理非 勇武缺一不可<br />\n不分化 不割席<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7ab8e34d64fcaf2d1efcad487b507d5b6496fc9","tid":1466661,"uid":262346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:51:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dba622880854f4dae393340dfcbe3ed1a3788113","tid":1466661,"uid":262346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:51:39.000Z","msg":"推"}]}